text:
Lastly, I'll confirm tomorrow. I'll pick you up in the
morning by car. Kogane, Yuika, and Kiriko, in that order

We'll have plenty of time to get ready because you have to dress up,
and we'll be meeting earlier than usual, so don't make a mistake.

After the live broadcast, we have a magazine shoot in the afternoon.
It's for the "Supporting New Life" issue, so it'll mainly feature spring outfits.

Hmm... Shooting both winter and spring in one day?
That's going to be tough, huh?

We usually stay ahead of the seasons, but with the increase
in live broadcasts during this time, it gets all mixed up.

Indeed...!
Let's make sure nobody becomes a "seasonal lost child".

Huh? Um, it's like...
a seasonal version of losing track of the days, I guess...?

Well~
that's a unique way of putting it.
